entries.femaleVariant: Why did he mention Morris all of a sudden?
Ohhh, that's right! This was a month before you came. Morris was already in the psycho ward by that time.
Morris was... a nosy little rat. Watched us through his blinds, snitched on us...
Popped eppy tabs like candy to stay awake every morning... The poor guy – turned out he had fatal insomnia.
Little did he know those tabs only sped up the process. Went into a real deep sleep just last week.
Finally – the fucking weasel. Good riddance.
